---
title: Zesty Beef & Black Bean Salad with Tortilla Chips, Sour Cream & Hot Sauce
description: Fajita-spiced dark meat chicken joins forces with black beans, tomato, and lime to make a salad that’s bursting with fresh flavors in a speedy 20 minutes. You’ll also bake up quick tortilla chips and serve on the side for dipping and scooping. Top it all off with sour cream and hot sauce, and you're in business (fast!).
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/67990b2635c238be91c9a87d-bd926fa0.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/679a72833b84bd9693c6cc76-en-US.pdf
time required: 20 minutes
